    </div>
    <div>
      <h4>Attendance Policy</h4>
      <h5>Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet, consectetur adipisicing elit, sed do eiusmod tempor incididunt ut labore et dolore magna aliqua. Ut enim ad minim veniam, quis nostrud exercitation ullamco laboris nisi ut aliquip ex ea commodo consequat. Duis aute irure dolor in reprehenderit in voluptate velit esse cillum dolore eu fugiat nulla pariatur. Excepteur sint occaecat cupidatat non proident, sunt in culpa qui officia deserunt mollit anim id est laborum.</h5>
    </div>
    <div class="form-group checkbox-group required">
      <label>Member Commitment Policy</label><br>
      <input type="checkbox" name="question[policy]" value="1">      I have read and agree to the policy.  <br>
      <small class="form-text text-muted">This is mandatory.</small>
    </div>
    <div class="form-group checkbox-group required">
      <label>Attendance Policy</label><br>
      <input type="checkbox" name="question[policy]" value="1">      I have read and agree to the policy.  <br>
      <small class="form-text text-muted">This is mandatory.</small>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="tab">
    <div class="form-group radio-group required" id="jump-group2">
      <label>Returning or New</label><br>
      <input type="radio" name="question[returning]" value="Returning">      Returning  <br>
      <input type="radio" name="question[returning]" value="New">      New  <br>
      <small class="form-text text-muted">Select Yes if you are a returning tutor.</small>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="tab" id="jump-group3">
    <div class="form-group radio-group required">
      <label>Prefer to work with previous student or class?</label><br>
      <input type="radio" name="question[prev_again]" value="Yes">      Yes  <br>
      <input type="radio" name="question[prev_again]" value="No">      No  <br>
      <small class="form-text text-muted">Select Yes if you want to be matched up with previous student or class.</small>
    </div>
      <div class="form-group">
        <label for="question[preference]">Preferred Student/Class</label>
        <input type="text" name="question[preference]" class="form-control">
        <small class="form-text text-muted">Please write down the name of the student or class.</small>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="tab">
      <h4>Public Service Center Volunteer Questions</h4>
      <div class="form-group required">
        <label for="question[volunteer]">PSC Q1</label>
        <input type="text" name="question[volunteer]" class="form-control" placeholder="ex. First Middle Last">
        <small class="form-text text-muted">Please enter your full name here!</small>
      </div>
      <div class="form-group required">
        <label for="question[volEmail]">PSC Q2</label>
        <input type="email" name="question[volEmail]" class="form-control" placeholder="ex. TMC@gmail.com">
        <small class="form-text text-muted">We'll never share your email with anyone else.</small>
      </div>
      <div class="form-group required">
        <label for="question[sid2]">PSC Q3</label>
        <input type="text" name="question[sid2]" class="form-control" placeholder="ex. 3032179600">
        <small class="form-text text-muted">Please enter your SID here!</small>
      </div>
  </div>
  <div class="tab">
    <div class="form-group">
      <label for="comment">Comments</label>
      <input type="text" name="question[comment]" class="form-control">
      <small class="form-text text-muted">Special instructions / Preference</small>
    </div>
  </div>

